* fwdsp-mgr should ensure fwdsp is always running by restarting it as needed.
* fwdsp should maintain all configured pipelines
  - If immortal, ensure the pipeline is always running\
  - Otherwise, ensure on-demand pipelines start/pause/stop as needed

- Pipeline types
  - capture: Receive audio from sound devices
  - sender: Sends audio to sound devices
  - recoder: Transcodes audio between stream formats
